Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这东京都内的投票站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从早上开始就聚集了大量的选民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:09.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,等待投票的队伍排成了长龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在樱庭总理的呼吁下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,付诸实施的偶像禁止法案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:21.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算是静香也会紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:32.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,能做的事情我们都已经做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:33.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:55.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:57.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,选举结果已经出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:00.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,害怕知道结果?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好啦 奶奶会陪在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:05.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:09.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:21.13,Idol_Jihen_main_up,,0,0,0,,国民对于偶像议员的活动究竟会做出怎样的判断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:00:59.92,Idol_Jihen_main_up,,0,0,0,,最新的舆论调查显示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.09,Idol_Jihen_main_up,,0,0,0,,各党的支持率没有大幅度的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.18,Idol_Jihen_main_up,,0,0,0,,这次选举的支持与否究竟会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:12.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就在刚才国民投票的开票结果出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:12.17,Idol_Jihen_screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}“偶像议员禁止法案”开票速报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:15.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在的开票率是80%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,结果显示 偶像议员禁止法案…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.25,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为您现场报道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:57.07,Idol_Jihen_title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,500)\pos(1198.534,586)\blur2}事变11   正式Live的5秒前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,得知刚刚的投票结果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:00.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在楼凯党这正欢呼雀跃着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:07.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总理 偶像议员禁止法通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:08.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你现在的心情是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,曾经说过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:14.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我对偶像的存在并不反对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是身为肩负国政的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为太过热衷于偶像活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:25.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,而忽略了本职 这是本末倒置了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:27.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这个层面上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:34.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这次投票中 我感受到了国民十分贤明的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请问对于被称作偶像议员她们的今后 做何想法?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这就不用说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只要做本来该做的事情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没想到我们的作战被反过来利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,实在是失策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为我太忘乎所以 煽动大家朝着错误的方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现到如今说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可事实就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:14.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只为了取胜的表演是无法感动人心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:21.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看了那场表演的观众们…国民们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:25.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,会否定我们偶像议员是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:30.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我什么都没有看清…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要逃跑吗? 静!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,千夏 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,责怪静是没有道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:49.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在我们应该做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,严肃接受这次的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,考虑今后的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:56.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总之 我会负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗? 包在她身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:18.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我相信她们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:19.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,感觉很冷清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:35.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,像是世界上的灯全都熄灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:39.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,即使打开广播也听不到歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:45.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这也是那个偶像议员禁止法案的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,即便如此每天也这样过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:56.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是我没能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我的身体…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,喂 夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大白天的犯什么懒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,快来帮爷爷处理田里的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:38.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你往那里耕作在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要耕的地方在这里吧 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事啦 没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:58.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,三平 你也不要太啰嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不然是不会受女孩子欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:01.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了 夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.07,Idol_Jihen_screen,,0,0,0,,偶像议员禁止法案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.07,Idol_Jihen_screen,,0,0,0,,对违反者进行罚规探讨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.07,Idol_Jihen_screen,,0,0,0,,甚至剥夺议员资格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不吃一点的话对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:18.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:39.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了 不好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:47.25,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明明都这个时候了 还感觉很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:53.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我如果没有当什么偶像议员就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,像一直以来那样普通地生活的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就不会有这样的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在的我 要让别人露出微笑什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:08.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来 擦下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:22.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 你听说过三日月神乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:24.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听过一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你知道她是日本第一位偶像议员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:30.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,已经是20年以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这个国家陷入黑暗的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,三日月神乐出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一开始大家都嘲笑她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:44.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,年轻的姑娘 仅仅一个人能做到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一开始是一场孤独的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 终于一位又一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:56.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,神乐的身边聚集了相同想法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,成为总理大臣的三日月神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,改变了这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,带领陷入黑暗的国家走向充满希望的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,三日月总理曾经那么得厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:12.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,曾是个好时代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:20.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有一次 被问及为什么要成为偶像议员的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她这么回答道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,想要让别人露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么 那个三日月神乐现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 那个时候的三日月神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:38.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 和现在的你是同岁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:43.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,和你一样年轻的女孩 相信自己战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月怎么可能会做不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 我不是什么三日月神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我什么都没能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没能让任何人露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:03.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么 用你的眼睛确认下不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,用我的眼睛确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:15.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这种地方要确认什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星菜议员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你把我忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是我啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,难道说 是后补选举时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:34.25,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好久不见 我是鹭宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:37.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您在这里做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,站前的打扫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为了下次的选举做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,希望选民们能够记住我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:49.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,想到要改变些什么 首先要从自己身边的事做起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员禁止法案的事情我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:11:00.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但并不是全部的国民反对偶像议员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不要气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鹭宫先生 您现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不属于任何党派姑且工作着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算不在楼凯党那样的大党里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只要有志向就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为 教会我这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不就是你吗 星菜议员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,做好觉悟等我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:29.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,下次选举可不会输给你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:39.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,走好 星菜议员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:55.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,姐姐在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:03.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为表情看起来很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在担心我吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:10.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,给 是我亲手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:14.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是吃了会精神的饭团哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是星菜夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:23.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从好久以前就是鬼丸小姐的粉丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:26.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:40.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,艺术品是不会跑走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星菜议员 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,古里议员 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:55.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那件事之后 这里在网上什么的地方成了热门话题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:13:00.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以干脆把垃圾场变成了现在艺术美术馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是听说就是因为这个有很多垃圾处理不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 以前确实那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过 现在完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,靠的是回收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让村里的人彻底进行了垃圾回收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,然后渐渐的垃圾减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一开始不知道会变得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还是要先把能做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:30.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您知道吗 江户时代的垃圾回收率有90%以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,以这个为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:44.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一开始猫变得太多 造成了挺大的困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:48.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过从能做的开始做起 什么都能改变哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:52.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在猫住的公寓已经建好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,状态还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是吧 猫老大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,志愿者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:02.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,喜欢这海的冲浪者们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,帮我们召集了伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:10.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一步一个脚印 慢慢积累不断改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:13.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,多亏这样现在已经变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为了保护这海原本的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,今后我们也会加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幼儿园有办下去的希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为那件事得知关门的地方企业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,愿意出资运营资金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,工作的妈妈们和孩子们也松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星菜议员 请让我再次向您表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要是没和您相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:49.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我可能现在还是老体制下楼凯党的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:54.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但现在 我真心觉得能成为国会议员是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:59.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从身边的事开始改变 才会有现在这么大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:13.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以啊 用你的眼去确认下不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,奶奶 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有答案了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,离开赞来党的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我非常恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:38.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但现在想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:41.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个时候我只是单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:42.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,单相思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:48.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只是把自己的要求强加于别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,既不给于 也不接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,带着自命清高的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对周围人回应不了自己而感到焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,到最后都不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:06.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明明人不是一个人活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,却自以为一个人能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:14.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是她改变了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一开始觉得 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没脑子 走哪算哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:27.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一直说些梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过她总是不求回报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:37.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,给予我笑容 勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,终于找到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那就别害怕了 相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为她是你选择的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:18.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要出门?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:20.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要去找夏月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你看 我就说没事的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以不是早说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:32.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们之间的联系没有这么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,到这个时候还害羞个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,之前的事 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:55.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明明大家都在努力 我却一个人逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我才是应该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:06.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,纠结赢下比赛 却忘记了重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们无论何时都要传递笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:13.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月会离开也是自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是不是 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:22.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个 不过多亏了这事我才明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:25.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我要先让静露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我发现了 为了让大家露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:33.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,首先要让身边的人笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:37.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我一直都依靠着静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没能让静露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以先要让静露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:46.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想看到静的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:51.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以 今后也请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星菜夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你就是我的搭档 不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:13.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 把笑容传递给大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,再以with的身份来一次live
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:21.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这就不好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:28.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这个节骨眼上 搞违反偶像议员禁止法的事可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:34.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,确实偶像议员禁止法得到了全民投票的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:39.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 并不是全部的人都反对偶像议员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:43.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,肯定也有支持我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:46.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,党首 您说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢夏月这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,党首…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静 你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只要粉丝还在 就要唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这就是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:07.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,搞得不好的话 会被剥夺议员资格的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:08.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这不是为了我们自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是为了支持我的们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:15.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么我就尽全力让演唱会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我会让会场坐满观众的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样就决定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:31.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们俩组成组合的话 会场肯定会座无虚席
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,走吧 开始准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 多久没练习了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:42.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…7天?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:46.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,休息7天 表演的完成度也会跟着降低
